('94470','32541','5','Country house in elegant style near Manacor for sale'),
('94471','32542','5','This chic and very well maintained villa, in the elegant country house style, stands on a ca 16.000m² of land with panoramic views. The city Manacor and several golf courses are nearby. The house has approx 350m² of living space. On the main level are, a living-dining room, open country kitchen with utility room, guest bedroom, guest toilette & shower, large office space with access to the garden, and master bedroom with spacious bathroom en suite. From the living room and the kitchen you have access to a partly covered terrace chill.\r\nIn the basement is a guest apartment and a sauna area with access to the garden aswella technik room and a cellar. The guest apartment consists of a small living room with kitchenette, 2 bedrooms, a bathroom and a toilet. Furthermore there is a separate guest bedroom with kitchinette and bathroom. The Mediterranean landscaped garden is automatically irrigated with water from their own wells. The house is powered via the main red and photovoltaic power. Gas central heating ensures even on cooler days for the right temperature. An outdoor swimming pool with terrace, in the midst of beautifully landscaped and easy to maintain garden completes the offer.\r\n'),
